title: The Daily Show Presents: Desi Lydic Abroad – How Did Namibia Accomplish So Much So Quickly?
itunes:title: The Daily Show Presents: Desi Lydic Abroad – How Did Namibia Accomplish So Much So Quickly?
description:
Desi Lydic travels to Namibia -- one of the youngest countries on the planet, which was ranked 13th on the 2017 Global Gender Gap Report -- to investigate the steps it's taken toward equality.
